text: Eoacmaea calamus is a species of sea snail, a true limpet, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Eoacmaeidae, one of the families of true limpets. ==Description== ==Distribution== ==References== ==External links== * Category:Eoacmaeidae Category:Gastropods described in 1864 * https://molluscsoftasmania.org.au/project/eoacmaea-calamus/
title: Eoacmaea calamus
